SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 2018 as follows:
1. On Page 6, Line 16, by inserting after the word “redevelopment” and before the word
“receiving”, the words “that has been allocated or that is”;
2. On Page 17, Line 23, by inserting after the number “2027” and before the comma “,”, the words
“and upon the property being placed on the tax rolls”;
3. On Page 18, Line 2, by inserting after the word “years” and before the word “or”, the words
“after the completion of construction”;
4. On Page 18, Line 2, by deleting after the word “the” and before the word “property”, the words
“transfer of such”; and
5. On Page 18, Line 2, by inserting after the word “property” and before the comma “,”, the words
“is conveyed to an unrelated third party bona fide purchaser”;
